data.description: Charming three-bedroom, two-bath home with a cozy fireplace in a highly sought-after neighborhood. This lovely property is conveniently located close to Franklin Highschool, providing easy access to major stores and great schools. With its desirable features and excellent location (half a block from Resler), this home presents a fantastic opportunity at an excellent price. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your dream home. Contact us today for more information or to schedule a viewing.
